<TEXT>
Friday nights are heavy on comedy and gardening. The BBC is currently
offering repeats of Only Fools And Horses where Del has plans for a
satellite TV company (8.00 BBC1); Red Dwarf, which now moves on to Series II
and introduces its best character, the robot Kryten (9.00 BBC2); and
