from the Renaissance onwards (9.00). As that ends BBC2 begins a new series
of Gardeners' World (9.30). Items include a dried herbaceous border created
by gardening photographer Andrew Lawson.
Friday is also film night. Best bet is the Clint Eastwood western High
Plains Drifter (10.20 BBC1) which, even in 1972, had all the violence and
vague supernaturalism that became Eastwood's trademarks.
