<DATELINE>
   STOCKHOLM
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Pharmacia, the majority state-owned Swedish pharmaceutical group, is seeking
a buyer for Pharmacia Deltec, a wholly-owned US subsidiary manufacturing
home drug delivery systems, writes Hugh Carnegy in Stockholm.
Pharmacia, due to be fully privatised this year, said the sale was in line
