<HEADLINE>
FT  17 FEB 94 / World News in Brief: Queen to visit Russia
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Queen will later this year become the first reigning British monarch to
visit Russia since the 1917 revolution, in a move aimed at setting the seal
on closer relations between London and Moscow.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>RUZ  Russia, East Europe.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P9111 Executive Offices.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
