FT  16 FEB 94 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1993/94
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (80).
BREWERIES (1) Fuller STA, BUILDING &amp; CNSTRN (4) Ashtead, Howard, Spandex,
